            <note xml:id="foot.f2">See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-11775.xml">letter from F. S. Arnold, [2]6 December 1878</ref> and n. 2. CD refers to passages in <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_6019.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> 6th ed.</ref>, pp. 86 and 89.</note>
        </div>    
        
